	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bu.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>不但⋯⋯，而且⋯⋯ (bùdàn..., érqiě...) is a very commonly used pattern that indicates "not only, ... but also...."
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
